      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·魏風·002.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">汾沮洳.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>彼汾沮洳，言采其莫。彼其之子，美無度；美無度，殊異乎公路。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There in the oozy grounds of the Fen,
They gather the sorrel.
That officer,
Is elegant beyond measure.
He is elegant beyond measure.
But, perhaps, he is not what the superintendent of the ruler's carriages ought to be.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-weifeng-state-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879-fulltext">
