      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·魏風·002.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">汾沮洳.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>彼汾一曲，言采其藚。彼其之子，美如玉；美如玉，殊異乎公族。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There along the bend of the Fen,
They gather the ox-lips.
That officer,
Is elegant as a gem.
He is elegant as a gem;
But, perhaps, he is not what the superintendent of the ruler's relations should be.</seg>
      </tuv>
